{"tid":959606,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自言冇夾過但填海睇法與劉德華一樣 林鄭：祝華仔演唱會成功","createTime":"2018-12-28T17:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T10:10:22.000Z","uid":20058,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2af959712b2ac5d41a231a3e5d998f755a9a15ea","tid":959606,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T17:33:50.000Z","msg":"團結香港基金早前推出以藝人劉德華旁白的短片，力撐東大嶼填海計劃，強調「啱就要去做」，被批評與其海洋公園保育基金保育大使身份有矛盾。特首林鄭月娥今午出席施政報告記者會時，指該短片上載前大約兩日，她率先看過，看完後很驚訝，因為短片與其施政報告的理念以至用字，例如「前行、希望、要行就行」等，都十分吻合，但她強調「冇夾過」，認為原因可能是自己同「華仔」都生長於同一個年代，「或者我大佢幾年」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n她指與華仔一樣，生於基層，受惠於香港發展，華仔在演藝界成功，2人都關顧下一代，想下一代「有呢個機會」，基於同樣考慮，她稱自己也希望大家堅定前行。不過，她認為，該短片推出後，社交媒體出現對劉德華的人身攻勢或侮辱，這並不公道，對他勇於表達意見表示敬佩，「最後預祝佢(華仔)12月演唱會成功」。<br />\n翻查資料，林鄭1957年出生，年屆61歲，劉德華比她年輕幾年，9月生日的他1961年出生，現年57歲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華仔早前曾透過公司發言人回應指，一直以來覺得香港土地不足，偶然機會下知道團結香港基金的「東大嶼大規模人工島方案」建議，經了解後覺得是積極可取的方案，所以義務擔任影片的旁白。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181010/58778127\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181010%2F58778127&d=kxjFbHuVRxYj3LxnLgn5xqEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=31239166\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181010%2F58778127&h=9141e857\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181010/58778127</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00962fc75625eb56185f9468770e680a795b2cff","tid":959606,"uid":92172,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T17:34:33.000Z","msg":"人善天不..."},{"pid":"76097ee03518f354ce162eb9870d053c111e5c99","tid":959606,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T18:24:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f497817077e57297c0527c69059374d62e11ef56","tid":959606,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T08:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b3dc6a7158172fcf47ec9986320a707f052b8d","tid":959606,"uid":89225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"00962fc75625eb56185f9468770e680a795b2cff","tid":959606,"uid":92172,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T17:34:33.000Z","msg":"人善天不..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:55:43.000Z","msg":"每種因果是有天修"},{"pid":"dea19b249dc8b80cdf2efb88d677278e735268ff","tid":959606,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又cut 2場 嘻嘻"},{"pid":"3d9fbac67dfc42729d3f8638b0e469f77bae39c2","tid":959606,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T10:05:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a484093c71819c94327bc8b45ce35f49b867c44","tid":959606,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T10:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}